{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/hofstadter-figure-figure-sequences","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"rosetta-code-challenges","demoType":null,"title":"Niz Hofstadter Figure-Figure","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Mfululizo wa Hofstadter Figure-Figure $R_n$ na $S_n$ unatolewa na</p>\n<p>$R_1 = 1\\ ;\\ S_1 = 2 \\\\R_n = R_{n-1} + S_{n-1}, \\quad n>1.$</p>\n<p>Hasa, mfululizo $R_n$ una thamani</p>\n<pre>1, 3, 7, 12, 18, ...</pre>\n<p>na mfululizo $S_n$ una thamani</p>\n<pre>2, 4, 5, 6, 8, ...</pre>\n<p>Niz $R_n$ definiše se rekurentnom relacijom $R_n = R_{n-1} + S_{n-1}$, dok je $S_n$ definisan kao niz pozitivnih celih brojeva koji se ne pojavljuju u nizu $R_n$.</p>\n</section>","id":"59622f89e4e137560018a40e","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Kreiraj dve funkcije nazvane <code>ffr</code> i <code>ffs</code> koje vraćaju <code>R(n)</code> ili <code>S(n)</code>, respektivno, za bilo koji primer <code>n</code>. Zapamtite da Hofstadter Figure-Figure sekvenca ima primer koji počinje od 1, sa $R_1 = 1$ i $S_1 = 2$.</p>\n<p>Hakuna thamani kubwa ya <code>n</code> inayopaswa kudhaniwa.</p>\n<p><strong>Vrati se</strong></p>\n<p>Rosetta: <a href='https://rosettacode.org/wiki/Hofstadter_Figure-Figure_sequences' target='_blank'>Niz Hofstadter Figure-Figure</a></p>.\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Rosetta","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"rosetta-code","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302286,"hooks":{"beforeAll":null,"beforeEach":"const ffrParamRes = [[10, 69], [50, 1509], [100, 5764], [1000, 526334]];\nconst ffsParamRes = [[10, 14], [50, 59], [100, 112], [1000, 1041]];","afterEach":null,"afterAll":null},"fields":{"slug":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/hofstadter-figure-figure-sequences"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function ffr(n) {\n  return n;\n}\n\nfunction ffs(n) {\n  return n;\n}","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>ffr</code> Trebalo bi da bude funkcija.</p>","testString":"assert(typeof ffr === 'function');"},{"text":"<p><code>ffs</code> Trebalo bi da bude funkcija.</p>","testString":"assert(typeof ffs === 'function');"},{"text":"<p><code>ffr</code> treba da vrati kompletan broj.</p>","testString":"assert(Number.isInteger(ffr(1)));"},{"text":"<p><code>ffs</code> trebalo bi da vrati kompletan broj.</p>","testString":"assert(Number.isInteger(ffs(1)));"},{"text":"<p><code>ffr(10)</code> inapaswa kurejesha <code>69</code></p>","testString":"assert.equal(ffr(ffrParamRes[0][0]), ffrParamRes[0][1]);"},{"text":"<p><code>ffr(50)</code> inapaswa kurejesha <code>1509</code></p>","testString":"assert.equal(ffr(ffrParamRes[1][0]), ffrParamRes[1][1]);"},{"text":"<p><code>ffr(100)</code> inapaswa kurejesha <code>5764</code></p>","testString":"assert.equal(ffr(ffrParamRes[2][0]), ffrParamRes[2][1]);"},{"text":"<p><code>ffr(1000)</code> treba da restaurira <code>526334</code></p>","testString":"assert.equal(ffr(ffrParamRes[3][0]), ffrParamRes[3][1]);"},{"text":"<p><code>ffs(10)</code> inapaswa kurejesha <code>14</code></p>","testString":"assert.equal(ffs(ffsParamRes[0][0]), ffsParamRes[0][1]);"},{"text":"<p><code>ffs(50)</code> treba da restaurira <code>59</code></p>","testString":"assert.equal(ffs(ffsParamRes[1][0]), ffsParamRes[1][1]);"},{"text":"<p><code>ffs(100)</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>112</code></p>","testString":"assert.equal(ffs(ffsParamRes[2][0]), ffsParamRes[2][1]);"},{"text":"<p><code>ffs(1000)</code> treba da restaurira <code>1041</code></p>","testString":"assert.equal(ffs(ffsParamRes[3][0]), ffsParamRes[3][1]);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/rosetta-code/#rosetta-code-challenges","dashedName":"hofstadter-figure-figure-sequences","certification":"rosetta-code","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"rosetta-code","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"rosetta-code-challenges","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/hofstadter-q-sequence","prevChallengePath":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/heronian-triangles","id":"59622f89e4e137560018a40e","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function ZigZagMatrix(n) {\n  const mtx = [];\n  for (let i = 0; i < n; i++) {\n    mtx[i] = [];\n  }\n\n  let i = 1;\n  let j = 1;\n  for (let e = 0; e < n * n; e++) {\n    mtx[i - 1][j - 1] = e;\n    if ((i + j) % 2 === 0) {\n      // Even stripes\n      if (j < n) j++;\n      else i += 2;\n      if (i > 1) i--;\n    } else {\n      // Odd stripes\n      if (i < n) i++;\n      else j += 2;\n      if (j > 1) j--;\n    }\n  }\n  return mtx;\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/hofstadter-figure-figure-sequences"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}